<template>

</template>

<script>
  
export default {
    created() {
    var scripts = [
      "https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/alpinejs/alpine@v2.x.x/dist/alpine.min.js",
      "js/local.js"
    ];
    scripts.forEach(script => {
      let tag = document.createElement("script");
      tag.setAttribute("src", script);
      document.head.appendChild(tag);
    });
  }
}
</script>

</style>
